Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  隔壁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐那位置肯定會天天睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  離我家很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長怎麼定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都還不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用猜拳或者抽籤更妥當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像個成熟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千打架可厲害了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺她與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同學笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得更科同學最適合做班長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真讓我大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然叫自己小千
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺她好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥君笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}開始嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪子布！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你說小千的壞話！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙  沙織並沒有說她壞話的意思  對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是說她怪怪的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不是壞話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己的性格也好不到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}手舉起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  到此為止到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了桃子  來個深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（第三節體育課  換好衣服後到操場集合）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班變得好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  肚子餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生聚集在一起時  總覺得好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛偷偷摸摸地換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得跟女生一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒吃到教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  上次被打還記著仇呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那你臉紅什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}誰臉紅了 眼睛長哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}是是  寫在臉上了  都寫在臉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算到了世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你肯定能活到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真穗的弟弟挺可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把氣撒在飯上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一點也不臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你是真穗的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟的班級裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個叫千葉的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:07:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要參加社團活動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  也有直接回家的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師以前是哪個部的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}咦  你跟我一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美術部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}一起去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想過當美術老師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…有個喜歡的女孩在才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這種理由不也挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻君是籃球部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想長高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起打籃球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織叫我跟她去同一個部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  高槻君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家關係都好那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級的前輩叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千打架惹出禍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是找千葉同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經打過招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但被前輩們無視了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去要去參觀社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拽什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是打招呼什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢上完全勝過她們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是我告訴她們教室才弄成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我覺得這不怪二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然西丘第一小學很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那態度簡直讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉沙織就是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？小千喜歡那樣的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級生集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道幾點才能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說一年級生集合了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯了  是籃球部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  沙織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排球部還沒集合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  籃球部和排球部在同一個地方練習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐同學真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝指導
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好久沒三個人一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易分在同班  你們兩個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要和你們絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕交…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好…  要和好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是佐佐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那麼討厭我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記恨著對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前把你的弟弟錯當成女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你覺得修很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是修像我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直受小誠照顧  是一對的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你不覺得我們老師很棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概喜歡男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥不是這樣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你喜歡高槻同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是要好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是千葉同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人活得真壓抑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓抑？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是活著很壓抑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著很壓抑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等再去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小修先去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先洗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著很壓抑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.52,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HB3DBD8&}9{\1c&HD6B7F9&}個{\1c&HD8E0C1&}月{\1c&HEDC0CC&}前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.27,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HB3DBD8&}佳{\1c&HD6B7F9&}乃{\1c&HD8E0C1&}的{\1c&HECD6BC&}房{\1c&HEDC0CC&}間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來問高槻同學的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥同學向你告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥說了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更類似於我逼他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說喜歡他  讓他很困擾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真有默契
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會來這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不想見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來聽招人討厭的話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說過不知道來這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也討厭你這點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可說不出讓討厭自己的人喜歡自己這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有做什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分貝別這麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天覺得自己最可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也是  把我當成壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沒和佳乃一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  加奈子今天很早就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有社團活動的晨練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真的生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  那就只好…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和千葉同學和好不就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想去教室啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直躲在保健室也不是辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣就說出絕交這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但身在同班要不說話  還是有難度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把保健室當作旅館哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的  那傢伙真噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  今天有社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧  大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去社團嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今天不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概會被二年級盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要單獨一人的好  絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同學  幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同學挺直腰桿這麼說了那番話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我去叫佐佐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好帥  我也可以參加嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小千去的話  我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帥嗎？桃子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒帶錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子那份我來出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中生放學回家的路…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起回家的路…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟是如此的…如此的…開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓味  吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織  你不吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有資格這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織你又說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視她們的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家和她打招呼 是在無視我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信  那個一年級怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  那傢伙性格惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明天陪你一起去道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  更科同學笑過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用笑得這麼誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同學好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}小千差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥越來越喜歡她了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻君也說點什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
